<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="express-vt">express <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'spres/    美 /ɪk'spres/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>表达；表示：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Words can't express</strong> how excited I was!
我当时激动的心情难以言表。</p><footer>译林② – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ability to express an idea is as important as the idea itself.
表达观点的能力和观点本身同样重要。</p><footer>2011 湖南</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He cannot <strong>express himself</strong> clearly in English.
他不能用英语清楚地表达自己的意思。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On behalf of our school, I would like to express our warm welcome to you.
我代表我校，向您表示热烈的欢迎。</p><footer>2014 陕西书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="2ame">2.<strong>(AmE) 特快发送：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>express a package
把包裹特快发送</p></div></div>